text: Diana Dadabaeva (born 29 July 1991) is an Uzbekistani female water polo player. She was a member of the Uzbekistan women's national water polo team. She was a part of the team at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2010 Asian Games, 2011 World Aquatics Championships, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== *Sze Wai Yeung, Diana Dadabaeva - Asian Games zimbio *Uzbekistan's Diana Dadabaeva (L) throw getty Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani water polo players
